title: Chairtrend of the OverZeit Committee 7/30: Earthquake, Lakers, John Lewis, Inglewood
itunes:title: Chairtrend of the OverZeit Committee 7/30: Earthquake, Lakers, John Lewis, Inglewood
description:
On this edition of Chairtrend of the OverZeit Committee Jack and Miles discuss the 4.2 Earthquake in LA this morning, the NBA season starts back up today, John Lewis' funeral is happening today, and Inglewood is being gutted in certain areas to build a new stadium.
